          <title>Garrett Crochet agrees to $170 million, 6-year deal with Red Sox, AP source says</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Ace left-hander Garrett Crochet has agreed to a record-breaking $170 million, six-year contract with the Boston Red Sox, according to a person familiar with the negotiations. The person spoke to The Associated Press on Monday night on condition of anonymity because the deal had not been announced.]]></description>
